♪ Trinidad is nice

17:55.342 --> 17:57.544
♪ Trinidad is a paradise

17:57.577 --> 17:59.812
♪ Why, Trinidad is nice

17:59.846 --> 18:04.251
♪ Trinidad is a paradise

